{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"65383-la-fille-du-nom-de-norah","title":"La Fille Du Nom De Norah","description":"Norah loves her doll and gets worried one day when she is not able to find it.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"4","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Abdul Wahid","Marianne Pasy","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Melany  Pietersen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/65383-la-fille-du-nom-de-norah"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93398/size3/6e47cce5d03279405b1fe8c71a479888.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93398/size6/6e47cce5d03279405b1fe8c71a479888.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89675/size6/205bb1ba2a88d032555ad6f00785ca94.jpg","text":"Voici Norah, une petite fille.\nLe nom de sa poupée est Selah.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89676/size6/56377851799f3a1653c2b896e62f9795.jpg","text":"Norah adore sa poupée. Norah joue tous les jours avec Selah. Elle dort toutes les nuits avec sa poupée.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89677/size6/2cab924141498c90dc78020895211676.jpg","text":"Un jour, Norah ne trouva plus sa poupée. Elle la chercha partout, mais ne trouva Selah nulle part. Norah s'inquiéta.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89678/size6/d5cd3dabdfa06a9950ce69ab4b024bfa.jpg","text":"Norah ne savait pas que sa maman avait pris Selah pour la laver. La maman suspendit la poupée dehors, pour la faire sécher.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89679/size6/353d2783981288eaed23b62f953d5323.jpg","text":"\"Je ne trouve plus ma poupée\", pleura Norah. \"Ne t'inquiète pas\", lui dit sa maman.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89680/size6/6c95c2ea9185b6ac9a73b4dc2606a184.jpg","text":"Ce soir-là, la maman de Norah lui rendit sa poupée. La poupée était toute propre. On aurait dit que Selah était une poupée neuve!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89681/size6/7ce113f65c2f59a6597d7d79bc5a94e5.jpg","text":"Norah était tellement contente. Elle sautilla dans tous les sens. Elle dansa. Elle rit aux éclats.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89682/size6/212f2164440a6f06f761176df74daf97.jpg","text":"Et elle remercia sa maman.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":134}}